#### Nesting happens in routing
* Before:
<%= ruby_begin %>
# config/routes.rb
  resources :posts
  resources :comments
<%= ruby_end %>
* After:
<%= ruby_begin %>
# config/routes.rb
  resources :posts do
    resources :comments
  end
<%= ruby_end %>

